        "description": "Description:\nEmbark on a thrilling adventure in \"Mighty Room,\" an immersive VR game where stealth, strategy, and cunning are your greatest allies. In this high-stakes game, your mission is to \"borrow\" valuable items from an enormous, high-tech space while avoiding detection by the colossal room owner. Experience a blend of suspense, excitement, and futuristic innovation as you navigate through a vast and intricate environment.\n\nGame Features:\n\n    Immersive VR Environment:\n        Dive into a meticulously designed world with cutting-edge VR graphics that make you feel like you're truly inside a colossal, high-tech room. Every corner, shadow, and detail is crafted to enhance your immersive experience.\n\n    Stealth and Strategy Gameplay:\n        Engage in heart-pounding stealth gameplay where every move matters. Use your intelligence and agility to stay hidden, create distractions, and outmaneuver the vigilant room owner.",
